name: WorldEvent.Load
description: WorldEvent.Load is fired when Minecraft loads a world. This event is fired when a world is loaded in ClientLevel(ClientPacketListener, ClientLevel.ClientLevelData, ResourceKey, DimensionType, int, Supplier, LevelRenderer, boolean, long) , MinecraftServer#createLevels(ChunkProgressListener) . This event is not Cancelable . This event does not have a result. Event.HasResult This event is fired on the MinecraftForge.EVENT_BUS .
